verbose_text: Several post-translational modifications have been described for IAV proteins, including the glycosylation of HA and NA [XREF_BIBR], the palmitoylation (S acylation) of HA and M2, and the SUMOylation (i.e., conjugation with the small ubiquitin like modifier) of M1 [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR], NS1 [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR], NP [XREF_BIBR], PB1 [XREF_BIBR], and NEP / NS2 [XREF_BIBR] (' Post-translational processing ' in Figure XREF_FIG).
